Some notes before you proceed:

· Make sure that you're on the latest stable version of Magisk. This won't work if you're on some other half-assed root solution;
· Make sure the file isn't bigger than 256Mb;
· If you're flashing a zip that wipes or replaces /system or /vendor in any way… well thar be dragons, and I don't think you should proceed for safety reasons
